{"tid":1468874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 689 發出重要提示","createTime":"2019-08-13T22:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T22:49:04.000Z","uid":272630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f83b3a5d96696b3323733e3cb9d2d77dd59f6445","tid":1468874,"uid":272630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:33:04.000Z","msg":"無待堂：敵方好想你割，你會唔會俾佢得逞啊～～<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68585251_2345785362173862_5391613489099833344_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQkWOFzk2CVaCNuVg6_WXl1OYvnCNXFW4y__2ekZ3gWwLB0qtcmnyY_a8MITaQgJa20&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=b64c0e5ff6e3ee99d86cb098bbf11cd0&amp;oe=5E15F755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68585251_2345785362173862_5391613489099833344_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQkWOFzk2CVaCNuVg6_WXl1OYvnCNXFW4y__2ekZ3gWwLB0qtcmnyY_a8MITaQgJa20%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Db64c0e5ff6e3ee99d86cb098bbf11cd0%26oe%3D5E15F755&h=ce7cdb64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想同大家講個關於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「四面楚歌」</span></strong>既故仔。話說劉邦同項羽打仗，打到中後段，為左瓦解楚軍既鬥志，劉邦叫漢軍唱楚國歌曲，令楚軍以為漢軍已經盡佔左楚地。項軍聽到中伏，以為自己形勢真係咁差，跟住the rest is history。<br />\n<br />\n咁想講咩呢？其實就係坊間、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>網絡好多「今次失分喇」、「今次中計喇」、「今次死喇」</strong></span>之類，扮成和理非黃絲既「網民」，其實都係中共既人，三人成虎，只要你俾呢d語言包圍，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要意志唔夠堅定，就會好似楚軍咁以為自己真係已經輸哂</strong></span>。警察恐怖，但唔係致命，心戰先攞命。警察可以令你輸一場戰役，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心戰可以令你輸一場戰爭</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n對面都講到明係要「和平示威者」同激進派割席。你唔割，佢咪放d人落黎吹道歉、割席，影響到你班人都覺得要割囉。你估佢地識放人落黎衝，就唔識放人落黎扮割席咩？唔撚好俾呢敵軍既心戰動搖到，你未必贏，但至少唔會自己輸先。<br />\n<br />\n＃認同請分享<br />\n＃停一停諗一諗<br />\n＃果d真係自己友咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dadazim/posts/2345730992179299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdadazim%2Fposts%2F2345730992179299&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ae971083\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dadazim/posts/2345730992179299</a>"},{"pid":"93946048b4be4630d46e303b45e55bf1157aff9d","tid":1468874,"uid":152584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:34:11.000Z","msg":"星期日民陣遊行喺最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23e672f40d896a96e1913d41213b5622916406e","tid":1468874,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8e7635970d57996a1583fbf16f6da217e323a","tid":1468874,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:48:41.000Z","msg":"班狗咪暴徒囉！唔係輕聲係耳邊講，係大大用力去講&quot;解斯香港警隊&quot;"},{"pid":"be66d9c2a0be67838d04f7d405552c7aefb5b866","tid":1468874,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28e8e7635970d57996a1583fbf16f6da217e323a","tid":1468874,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:48:41.000Z","msg":"班狗咪暴徒囉！唔係輕聲係耳邊講，係大大用力去講&quot;解斯香港警隊&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:49:04.000Z","msg":"狗咪暴徒囉！唔係輕聲係耳邊講，係大大用力去講&quot;解散香港警隊&quot;"}]}